    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1212">
<l>kayaluṇkaṇ yāṉirappat tuñciṟ kalantārk </l>
<l> kuyaluṇmai cāṟṟuvēṉ maṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If my fish-like painted eyes should, at my begging, close in sleep, I could fully relate my sufferings to my lord.</l>
            </lg>
